Pi (https://github.com/earendil-works/pi-mono)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The bundled Pi SDK is built from these npm packages:

    @earendil-works/pi-agent-core
    @earendil-works/pi-ai
    @earendil-works/pi-coding-agent
    @earendil-works/pi-tui

The compiled bundle is shipped at:

    apps/vscode/resources/pi-sdk/bootstrap.js

Build artifacts are produced by `packages/agent/pi-sdk/build.bootstrap.mjs`
from the upstream Pi packages at the version declared in
`packages/agent/pi-sdk/package.json`.

================================================================================
Runtime dependencies
================================================================================

Runtime dependencies installed via pnpm are gated through the
`pnpm check:security` script, which validates each dependency against an
allow-list of permissive licenses:

    MIT, ISC, Apache-2.0, BSD-2-Clause, BSD-3-Clause, CC0-1.0, CC-BY-4.0,
    0BSD, Unlicense, Python-2.0, BlueOak-1.0.0

To regenerate a full attribution list of installed dependencies, run:

    pnpm exec license-checker-rseidelsohn --production --csv

